cross: Paphiopedilum Shin Yi's Pride x Paphiopedilum Johanna Burkhardt

measurements.description: Four flowers crowded on a 27.1-cm inflorescence; dorsal sepal chartreuse, striped mahogany, diffuse centrally; synsepal chartreuse, striped mahogany; petals hirsute edges, chartreuse, mahogany spots basally, fusing to dark mahogany distally; pouch charteuse, partially overlaid light brown; staminode light yellow, mahogany sides, canescent; substance firm; texture matte.
